  "body": "<p>Loved using this months kits from Studio Calico, Planetarium. Here's how this layout came together using the main kit only.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1a-DSC_1165-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cd6a0a013f3f13db.jpg?v=1782538185\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1b-DSC_1166-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/79d83b1aeccf807e.jpg?v=1782538188\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1c-DSC_1167-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/db30bba45571f45a.jpg?v=1782538190\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1d-DSC_1168-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d9b673a7441b717a.jpg?v=1782538193\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1e-DSC_1169-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3b048b8cd3710875.jpg?v=1782538196\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1f-DSC_1170-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/dc03b00343e0f143.jpg?v=1782538199\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1g-amy_sc_may_1-600x438.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/de1f977ffe6f01f6.jpg?v=1782538202\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1g-amy_sc_may-560x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/69a215e6940803d4.jpg?v=1782538204\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I made quite a few layouts using these awesome kits, which you can view in the gallery. Ironically I am also headed from Perth to Melbourne tomorrow. Can't wait to see some of you at Better Homes &amp; Gardens LIVE!</p>"
